Description: Core C++ engine for lmebayes: envelope-based iid samplers,
    two-block Gibbs mixed-model engines, and optional OpenCL acceleration.
    Full-featured developer backend for lmebayes and extensions. End users
    should use lmebayes for lmer/glmer-style mixed-model workflows.
License: GPL-2
URL: https://github.com/knygren/lmebayesCore
